title: Dont.Be.Tardy.S03E05.Spring.Break.Forever.Biermanns.WEB-DL.x264-
description:
The sun is finally out as the Biermanns continue their Spring Break vacation in Destin, Florida, but their peace is disturbed by a couple of uninvited and unwelcomed guests. A trip to the boardwalk puts everyone in a good mood as Sweetie proves that you can never have too much fun. When Kim and Kroy go on a romantic date, Brielle tests the limits of her new found freedom

Thanks again To Rockter!
